description: '''Nicole Denise Cucco''' (born August 25, 2000), known professionally as '''Nicki Nicole''' ({{IPA|es|ˈniki niˈkol}}), is an [[Argentine]] rapper and singer-songwriter. Born and raised in [[Rosario, Santa Fe]], she gained popularity with her singles "Wapo Traketero", "[[Colocao]]", "[[Mamichula]]", "Mala Vida", and "[[Marisola]]" (remix).
